OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWorking women need greater 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmenopause rights - MPs     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Women going through menopause should be
OL,6, given greater rights and protection in 
OL,7, the workplace, MPs say.                
OL,9,FThe Women and Equalities Committee said
OL,10,Fa lack of support in the UK was pushing
OL,11,Fwomen out of work.                     
OL,13,FThe cross-party group wants menopause  
OL,14,Fto become a protected characteristic   
OL,15,Flike pregnancy, to give working women  
OL,16,Fmore rights.                           
OL,18,FOffering menopause leave should also be
OL,19,Fpiloted at a large public-sector       
OL,20,Femployer, the MPs said.                
